- Problem: dynamic import of @imgly/background-removal from jsDelivr failed
  with "Failed to fetch dynamically imported module" error
- Root cause: jsDelivr does not serve ESM + WASM with correct CORS headers
- Fix: switched CDN from jsdelivr → unpkg
- Added `publicPath` option pointing to unpkg so WASM model files resolve

